text: Hassan Louahid nicknamed Achour (14 March 1938 – 17 September 2020) was an Algerian international footballer and manager. He was born in Sétif, Algeria. He had 16 caps for the Algeria national team between 1965 to 1969. Achour died on 17 September 2020 in Algiers at the age of 82. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Algerian footballers Category:Algerian football managers
